 "html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Ek het vir 3 dae probeer om die beste sjokoladekoek te ontwikkel wat daar bestaan.  Dit moes iets tussen &#8216;n koek, &#8216;n mousse en &#8216;n brownie wees.  Hier is dit.</p>\n\n\n<div data-recipe-slot=\"1\"></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"760\" height=\"1024\" src=\"/media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3628-2-760x1024.jpg\" alt class=\"wp-image-6288\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3628-2-760x1025.jpg 760w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3628-2-600x809.jpg 600w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3628-2-223x300.jpg 223w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3628-2-768x1035.jpg 768w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3628-2-1139x1536.jpg 1139w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3628-2-750x1011.jpg 750w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3628-2-380x512.jpg 380w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3628-2-800x1079.jpg 800w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3628-2.jpg 1519w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" src=\"/media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3621-3-768x1024.jpg\" alt class=\"wp-image-6286\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3621-3-768x1024.jpg 768w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3621-3-600x800.jpg 600w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3621-3-225x300.jpg 225w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3621-3-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3621-3-750x1000.jpg 750w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3621-3-380x507.jpg 380w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3621-3-760x1013.jpg 760w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3621-3-800x1067.jpg 800w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3621-3.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"></figure></div>",
